import Container from "react-bootstrap/Container";
import Nav from "react-bootstrap/Nav";
import Navbar from "react-bootstrap/Navbar";
import NavDropdown from "react-bootstrap/NavDropdown";

const Header = () => {
  return (
    <header>
      <Navbar collapseOnSelect expand="lg" bg="dark" variant="dark">
        <Container>
          <Navbar.Brand href="#home">NetDot</Navbar.Brand>
          <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="responsive-navbar-nav" />
          <Navbar.Collapse id="responsive-navbar-nav">
            <Nav className="me-auto">
              <Nav.Link href="/MyPosts">My posts</Nav.Link>
              <Nav.Link href="/WorldPosts">World posts</Nav.Link>
              <NavDropdown title="This project" id="collasible-nav-dropdown">
                <NavDropdown.Item href="https://github.com/Zaccal">My github</NavDropdown.Item>
                <NavDropdown.Item href="https://github.com/Zaccal/NetDot">
                  This repositories
                </NavDropdown.Item>
                <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.3">
                  Something
                </NavDropdown.Item>
                <NavDropdown.Divider />
                <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.4">
                  Separated link
                </NavDropdown.Item>
              </NavDropdown>
            </Nav>
            <Nav>
              <Nav.Link href="#deets">More deets</Nav.Link>
              <Nav.Link eventKey={2} href="#memes">
                Dank memes
              </Nav.Link>
            </Nav>
          </Navbar.Collapse>
        </Container>
      </Navbar>
    </header>
  );
};

export default Header;
